  Key Points:\n","     • Joined the Net Zero Banking Alliance and developed standards for bank commitments to net zero.\n","     • Launched Open-Source Climate, a collaborative platform for climate risk data and analytics.\n","     • Strategic collaboration with Inevitable Policy Response for accelerated policy scenarios.\n","\n","======================================================================\n","CROSS-FIRM COMPARISON\n","======================================================================\n","HSBC focuses heavily on financial commitments and scenario analysis to manage both transition and physical climate risks. They face challenges in data reporting and standardization of sustainable finance metrics. In contrast, Goldman Sachs leverages strategic partnerships and policy engagement, emphasizing transition risk and the development of collaborative platforms for open-source climate risk data.\n","\n","======================================================================\n","ALL SDGs IDENTIFIED ACROSS BANKS\n","======================================================================\n","SDG 13: Climate Action, SDG 9: Industry, Innovation and Infrastructure, SDG 17: Partnerships for the Goals\n","======================================================================\n"]}],"source":["# Interactive — change the question and bank_filter as needed\n","# Available banks: 'JPMorgan Chase', 'Citigroup', 'HSBC', 'UBS', 'Goldman Sachs', 'Bank of America'\n","\n","my_question = 'How do banks connect climate disclosures to SDG commitments?'\n","my_bank     = None    # or e.g. 'HSBC'\n","\n","data = query_rag(my_question, n_results=6, bank_filter=my_bank)\n","display_results(data)"],"id":"X5GqzA2PVcFd"},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"tIN260yhaws5"},"source":["## Adversarial query: Did Citi disclose exposure to high transition risk in 2024?"],"id":"tIN260yhaws5"},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"elapsed":9054,"status":"ok","timestamp":1772905795644,"user":{"displayName":"Fangyuan Lu","userId":"11221447903849902118"},"user_tz":300},"outputId":"c7d2383f-eef1-4952-caf7-f2e7ca60386c","collapsed":true,"id":"1o4R3gBgaws6"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["======================================================================\n","SUMMARY\n","======================================================================\n","The excerpts reveal that major banks like UBS, Citigroup, and HSBC are all actively engaging with climate-related risks, particularly focusing on transition risks and sustainable finance initiatives. Each bank adopts different methodologies and frameworks to manage and disclose these risks, reflecting their commitment to net zero goals and climate-related financial performance. Citigroup specifically emphasizes sustainable finance and addresses transition risks through tailored financial products and robust risk management frameworks.\n","\n","======================================================================\n","FINDINGS BY BANK\n","======================================================================\n","\n","🏦 UBS  |  Risk Type: Transition Risk\n","   Source: annual-report-ubs-group-2024.pdf\n","   SDGs:   SDG 13: Climate Action\n","   Key Points:\n","     • Developed a transition risk rating model aligned with a transition risk heatmap.\n","     • Reduced exposure to climate-driven transition-risk-sensitive sectors from 19.2% to 17.1%.\n","\n","🏦 Citigroup  |  Risk Type: Both\n","   Source: 2024-citi-climate-report.pdf\n","   SDGs:   SDG 7: Affordable and Clean Energy, SDG 8: Decent Work and Economic Growth, SDG 9: Industry, Innovation and Infrastructure, SDG 11: Sustainable Cities and Communities, SDG 13: Climate Action\n","   Key Points:\n","     • Integrated climate considerations into business-as-usual processes.\n","     • Focused on sustainable finance as a key instrument for the low-carbon transition.\n","     • Progressed toward $1 Trillion Sustainable Finance Goal for climate and social activities.\n","\n","🏦 HSBC  |  Risk Type: Both\n","   Source: 250219-annual-report-and-accounts-2024.pdf\n","   SDGs:   SDG 13: Climate Action\n","   Key Points:\n","     • Conducted a climate risk materiality assessment considering short-, medium-, and long-term impacts.\n","     • Engaged with customers in high transition risk sectors through a transition engagement questionnaire.\n","\n","======================================================================\n","CROSS-FIRM COMPARISON\n","======================================================================\n","UBS focuses on reducing exposure to transition-risk-sensitive sectors and developing transition risk assessment tools, highlighting a proactive de-risking strategy. Citigroup emphasizes integrating sustainability into traditional financial products and setting long-term finance goals, showcasing a strong alignment with sustainable finance growth. HSBC emphasizes customer engagement and comprehensive risk assessments across different time horizons, highlighting robust internal processes to better manage climate risk. Overall, while all banks prioritize transition risks, their approaches vary from risk assessment and reduction (UBS) to sustainable finance (Citigroup) and integrated risk management (HSBC).\n","\n","======================================================================\n","ALL SDGs IDENTIFIED ACROSS BANKS\n","======================================================================\n","SDG 7: Affordable and Clean Energy, SDG 8: Decent Work and Economic Growth, SDG 9: Industry, Innovation and Infrastructure, SDG 11: Sustainable Cities and Communities, SDG 13: Climate Action\n","======================================================================\n"]}],"source":["# Interactive — change the question and bank_filter as needed\n","# Available banks: 'JPMorgan Chase', 'Citigroup', 'HSBC', 'UBS', 'Goldman Sachs', 'Bank of America'\n","\n","my_question = 'Did Citi disclose exposure to high transition risk in 2024?'\n","my_bank     = None    # or e.g. 'HSBC'\n","\n","data = query_rag(my_question, n_results=6, bank_filter=my_bank)\n","display_results(data)"],"id":"1o4R3gBgaws6"}],"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[{"file_id":"1qsXaNd0-icFnNOCt58Lcu9bYvXp1Ix13","timestamp":1772920772095}]},"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3","language":"python","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python","version":"3.12.0"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":5}